Example to setup 2 sites on 2 ports
 80 - http://www.example.com 8080 - http://www.example.com:8080  Setup 2 ports Edit the /etc/apache2/ports.conf to add port number of Listen
Listen 80 Listen 8080 Edit the configuration file &lt;VirtualHost *:8080&gt; DocumentRoot /var/www/default &lt;/VirtualHost&gt;
